menu "SimCoupe SD Card (SDMMC)"

config SIM_SDCARD_ENABLED
    bool "Enable SDMMC SD card driver"
    default n
    help
        Enable the SDMMC SD card driver for SimCoupe.
        Mounts the SD card at /sdcard using 4-bit SDMMC bus (Slot 0).
        GPIO pins are hard-coded for Olimex ESP32-P4-PC:
          CLK=43, CMD=44, D0=39, D1=40, D2=41, D3=42.
        LDO_VO4 is enabled automatically to power the SDMMC IO pins.

endmenu
